data.description: Amazing 3 level townhome is move in ready! Great commuter location!! Spacious and open with lots of light! Recently painted in some areas with Harwood flooring and carpet! Large kitchen with bay window, stainless appliances, dining/ great room combo plus powder room complete this level. Up the stairs to 2 bedrooms and oversized master bedroom. Lower level has a bedroom, full bath and large rec room. Gas fireplace and door to fenced in back yard. Seller will finish painting for the new homeowners!  2 assigned parking spaces + 1 visitor. Closed to Rout 28 and I-66: Close to shopping-
